<item>
            <title>[SEC-1084] Retain Authentication.details when authenticating in LdapAuthenticationProvider</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-1084</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems that the LdapAuthenticationProvider looses any details set on the incomming Authentication.details property. Several other AuthenticationProviders retain these details&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unless of course this is intentional it should be trivial to improve this with simply copying the details, thus making them available to the application. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Simple suggestion attached as patch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
